OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK's first regular drug    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchecking service to launch 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A regular drug-checking service, aimed 
OL,6, at saving lives, is set to launch for  
OL,7, the first time in the UK.              
OL,9,FHarm-reduction charity, The Loop, will 
OL,10,Fbe offering a monthly drop-in drug     
OL,11,Ftesting service combined with health   
OL,12,Fadvice in Bristol from Saturday.       
OL,14,FLicensed by the Home Office, it will   
OL,15,Ffocus on dependent, frequent and       
OL,16,Fproblematic use.                       
OL,18,FIt is hoped the new scheme will reduce 
OL,19,Fdrug-related medical incidents,        
OL,20,Foverdoses and hospital admissions.     
